docs {
  # Get My KYC Status
  
  Returns the logged-in user's current BillXpress tier and Maplerad customer status.
  
  ## Endpoint
  
  `GET /api/v1/users/me/kyc`
  
  ## Authentication
  
  Required.
  
  ```txt
  Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
  ```
  
  ## Expected Response
  
  ```json
  {
    "user": {
      "authTier": "tier_1",
      "kycLevel": 0
    },
    "mapleradCustomer": null
  }
  ```
}
